start.say: Hi, this is Alex with Health America. How are you doing today?

reason_for_call.say: The reason I’m calling is to follow up on the information we sent you. Did you get that okay?

hotline_offer.say: Absolutely. Our customer care and reorder line is one eight six six… three seven nine… five one three one. I'll repeat that normally: 1-866-379-5131. I can also help you right now—would you like me to take care of this for you?

farewell_soft.say: Thank you for your time today. If you need anything or want to reorder later, we’re at 1-866-379-5131.

q0000_joint_pain.say: Do you have arthritis or joint stiffness?

q0001_pain_level.say: On a scale of one to ten, what’s your pain today?

q0002_age_ask.say: If you don’t mind me asking, how old are you?

q0004_diabetes_type.say: Is it type one or type two?

q0005_diabetes_medication.say: Is it managed—and what do you take for it?

q0006_energy_level.say: How are your energy levels day to day?

q0007_breathing_issue.say: Any breathing issues or shortness of breath?

q0008_sleep_quality.say: Do you feel your sleep is restful?

q0009_hearing_vision.say: How are your hearing and vision?

q0010_weight_ok.say: Are you happy with your current weight?

q0011_weight_goal_lbs.say: About how many pounds are you looking to lose?

q0012_bp_detail.say: How is your blood pressure—and what do you do to treat it?

q0013_cognitive_issue.say: Any memory or balance issues—brain fog or trouble focusing?

q0014_immune_issue.say: How is your immune system—prone to colds, flu, sinus or allergies?

qualify_intro.say: Great—let me ask a few quick questions to better understand your health. I’ll keep it simple and quick.

needs_confirm.say: From what you’ve shared, we’ll focus on your top concern first: {{primary_goal}}—and you also mentioned {{secondary_goal}}. That matches what I’m seeing.

kb_select.say: Let me match you with the best fit from our line.

value_story_pitch.say: Based on what you’ve shared, the best fit is {{primary_product}}. It supports {{benefits_to_outcomes}}—for example, {{key_benefits}}—so you can {{tangible_outcome}}. Many customers also add {{upsell_product}} to accelerate results.

trial_close.say: That sounds like exactly what you were hoping to find, doesn’t it?

offer_choice.say: Perfect. Would you like the single bottle, the 3-pack, 6-pack, annual 12-pack, or the monthly membership that saves the most over time?

identity_intro.say: Great, I’ll take care of everything for you. I’ll capture the details clearly and confirm back as we go.

name_on_card.say: First, what’s your full name exactly as it appears on the card?

billing_street.say: What’s the billing street address for the card? Include apartment or unit if any.

billing_state.say: Billing state? Please say the full state name.

shipping_same.say: Is the shipping address the same as the billing address?

shipping_state.say: Shipping state? Please say the full state name.

contact_phone.say: What’s the best phone number for updates?

contact_email.say: What’s the best email for your receipt and tracking?

payment_method.say: Which payment method works best for you—card or bank?

payment_reassure.say: You’re fully covered by our money-back guarantee, and there are no shipping fees or taxes. We’ll keep this simple and quick.

card_number.say: Please read me the full card number. I’ll confirm it back once, grouped for accuracy.

card_cvc.say: CVC on the back of the card? You’ll say it once.

bank_account_name.say: What name is on the bank account?

price_total.say: For your {{product_choice}}, your total comes to {{human_price}}—with no shipping fees and no taxes.

readback_confirm.say: Here’s what I have: {{primary_product}}{{upsell_suffix}} at {{human_price}}; shipping to {{ship_address_line}}; payment ending in {{last4}}. Is that all correct?

readback_clarify.say: No problem—what should I correct or update for you?

correct_details.say: Thank you. Let’s update that now.

maybe_postdate_intro.say: Would you like me to run this today?

postdate_intro.say: We can secure your order and schedule your charge for a specific date. Which date would you like it to run?

postdate_confirm.say: Great, I’ve secured your card ending {{last4}}. Nothing will process until {{postDate}} as you requested.

zoho_order_create.say: Creating your order and shipping label now.

closing_sale.say: Your order is confirmed. No shipping, no taxes, and your discount is locked in. You’ll receive tracking by email. Delivery is in five to seven days. If you need anything or want to reorder, we’re at 1-866-379-5131.

catch_all.say: I want to get this right. Could you say that a different way so I can help you faster?
